What is he doing so
early in the morning?

35
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:11,900
I know, but you could
have woken me up...

36
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:13,400
We live together!

37
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:17,270
All right. I'm on my way.
Let them wait.

38
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:23,010
Your storeroom blocks the
light, so I can't tell

39
