Is that why he was up until
three in the morning?

57
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:09,020
It's only a day trip, and he
was looking at Hakata.

58
00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:11,190
If we take the Shinkansen,
we can go there, and eat

59
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:13,060
ramen noodles, and come back within a day.

60
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:15,660
If you go there, you'll have to
come right back, won't you?

61
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,030
Give me back the paper.

62
00:04:19,030 --> 00:04:20,300
I want to read the
sports section.

63
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:22,100
I'm looking at the
culture section.

64
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:25,030
There's a special on
middle-aged couples' day off.

65
00:04:25,570 --> 00:04:26,870
I've had enough of this!

66
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:28,400
You'll tear the paper!

67
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,410
Hello!

68
00:04:31,910 --> 00:04:33,010
Mari!

69
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,110
I have to meet a friend,
so I just stopped by

70
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:36,980
