about where we're going.

71
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:39,820
You mean on our date?

72
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:42,050
How about Kamakura?

73
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:44,620
I was thinking the
same thing.

74
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:46,890
Here... I was reading
this article just now.

75
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,720
I read the same article.

76
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,660
That's why I thought of
going to Kamakura.

77
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,730
What a coincidence.

78
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:54,460
Do you think it's fate?

79
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,860
That's all I wanted to say.

80
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,300
We'll discuss the
details later.

81
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:58,630
Sorry to intrude.

82
