See you later.

83
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,070
Kamakura... ?

84
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:08,240
That takes the cake!
I'm speechless.

85
00:05:08,710 --> 00:05:09,940
Fate... ?

86
00:05:09,940 --> 00:05:11,710
Kamakura...
Here we come!

87
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:14,320
Kamakura... Kamakura...

88
